snippet.title: Los Lonely Boys - Heaven (Video Version)
snippet.description:
Los Lonely Boys' official music video for 'Heaven'. Click to listen to Los Lonely Boys on Spotify: http://smarturl.it/LLLSpot?IQid=LLBH

As featured on Playlist: The Very Best Of Los Lonely Boys. Click to buy the track or album via iTunes: http://smarturl.it/VBOLLLiTunes?IQid=LLBH
Google Play: http://smarturl.it/LLLHvnPlay?IQid=LLBH
Amazon: http://smarturl.it/VBOLLLamz?IQid=LLBH

More from Los Lonely Boys
More Than Love: https://youtu.be/6Zq2JAJVnuc
Diamonds: https://youtu.be/nSPGeEmoIQE

More great classic rock videos here: http://smarturl.it/ClassicRocks?IQid=LLBH

Follow Los Lonely Boys
Website: https://loslonelyboys.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/loslonelyboys
Twitter: https://twitter.com/loslonelyboys
Instagram: https://instagram.com/los_lonely_boys/

Subscribe to Los Lonely Boys on YouTube: http://smarturl.it/LLLsub?IQid=LLBH

---------

Lyrics:

Vamanos!

Save me from this prison
Lord, help me get away
'Cause only you can save me now
from this misery

I've been lost in my own place
and I'm getting' weary
How far is heaven?
And I know that I need to change
my ways of livin'
How far is heaven?
Lord, can you tell me?

I've been locked up way too long
in this crazy world.
How far is heaven?
And I just keep on prayin', Lord
And just keep on livin'.
